description: Delicious Argentinean cuisine is on the way with Parrillas on Wheels! Everything here is cooked to perfection, flavored with their very own seasonings and delicious Chimichurri sauce for that real Argentinean flavor. dry-aged meats seasoned 48 hours before they get to the grill ensure that every bite will be absolutely delicious when you visit this fantastic food truck!
name: Parrillas on Wheels
